msgid "# Set-ADReplicationSite"
msgstr "# Set-ADReplicationSite"

msgid "## SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "## 概述"

msgid "Sets the replication properties for an Active Directory site."
msgstr "设置 Active Directory 站点的复制属性。"

msgid "## SYNTAX"
msgstr "## 语法（Syntax）"

msgid "### Identity"
msgstr "### 身份"

msgid "### Instance"
msgstr "### 实例"

msgid "## DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "## 说明"

msgid ""
"The **Set-ADReplicationSite** cmdlet is used to set the properties for an Active Directory site that is being used for replication.\n"
"Sites are used in Active Directory to either enable clients to discover network resources (published shares, domain controllers) close to the physical location of a client computer or to reduce network traffic over wide area network (WAN) links.\n"
"Sites can also be used to optimize replication between domain controllers."
msgstr ""
"**Set-ADReplicationSite** cmdlet 用于设置用于复制的 Active Directory 站点的属性。在 Active "
"Directory 中，站点可用于使客户端能够发现位于其计算机物理位置附近的网络资源（已发布的共享资源、域控制器），或者减少通过广域网 (WAN) "
"链路传输的数据流量。站点还可以用于优化域控制器之间的复制过程。"

msgid "## EXAMPLES"
msgstr "## 示例"

msgid "### Example 1: Set the replication site to prevent connections"
msgstr "### 示例 1：设置复制站点以防止连接"

msgid ""
"The command sets the properties of the site with name NorthAmerica to "
"prevent its intersite topology generator (ISTG) at corp-DC02 from generating"
" connections for intersite replication."
msgstr "该命令设置了名为“NorthAmerica”的站点的属性，以防止位于corp-DC02的站点间拓扑生成器（ISTG）为站点间复制生成连接。"

msgid ""
"### Example 2: Set replication start times for a filtered list of sites"
msgstr "### 示例 2：为筛选后的站点列表设置复制开始时间"

msgid ""
"This command returns all the sites in the directory and sets the "
"**ScheduleHashingEnabled** property to spread replication start times "
"randomly across the entire schedule interval rather than just the first "
"quarter of the interval."
msgstr ""
"此命令会返回目录中的所有站点，并将 **ScheduleHashingEnabled** "
"属性设置为“随机分布复制开始时间”，从而使整个调度间隔内的复制开始时间均匀分布，而不仅仅是在该间隔的第一个季度内。"

msgid "### Example 3: Set the replication schedule for a site"
msgstr "### 示例 3：为某个站点设置复制计划"

msgid ""
"This example sets the daily replication schedule of the site with name Asia."
msgstr "这个例子设置了名为“Asia”的站点的每日复制计划。"

